{
  "stem": "3928.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's where I exchanged all the information, at-- at the time, when I worked at-- in Csepel Island.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, in-- as the war progressed, they started to-- to take all the young Jewish men and collecting them in camp, all in a military age group, not the older one, like the draft age, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And instead of the army, they put them in-- in work camp in Russia or in the country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't know really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I know they were in Russia a lot, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when they finished their jobs or wasn't useful anymore, I heard from many sources-- in fact, I heard from the Hungarian soldier.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, after we finish with them, we killed all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, we don't-- we don't need them anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what the heck we do with them?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to feed them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I find out the first horror, you know, of-- of-- of-- of what happened, you know to those people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was done, by the way, by the Hungarian Army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This wasn't the German Army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they did, at that time, I wasn't sure of it, because I just-- I had no contact, at the time, with the German authorities.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in 1939, 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Victory.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, as went on, and they took some people, even in menial job, like they-- they get pleasure out of it to taking doctors and attorneys and judges and put them like digging ditches and-- and making-- what they call-- bricks.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or just to dig ditches one day, cover up the next day, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I seen many of those people, because they use them, also, as, so to speak, slave laborers in the factory when I was working.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
